descriptionHTML:
Minimalistic analog watchface for your Android Wear smartwatch!

Radial Watch Face has a unique and simple design that uses optical illusion for drawing clock hands.
As time flies, a pulsing animation gives you a sense of every passing second.
It fits perfectly no matter if you have round or square smartwatch, it also contains mobile live wallpaper!

---

Supported smartwatches: LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, Motorola Moto 360, Sony SmartWatch 3, Asus ZenWatch, Samsung Gear Live.
